libobj is a library for parsing files in the Wavefront obj file format.

Inforamtion regarding copyright and this project see COPYING

For installation instructions see INSTALL.

Requirements:

This library requires std::tr1::shared_ptr support and can be provided in the
following ways.
- TR1 standard complient compiler. ie in <memory>
- GCC variant providing in <tr1/memory>
- Boost >= 1.31, see www.boost.org

The library will not build without one of the above

For targets not using the build system, define -DNO_POSIX_READ -DYYNO_UNISTD_H
